  "detailed_description": "<h1>Patch Note</h1><p><strong>[Patch 2020.06.26]</strong><br>-Add Chinese.<br><br><strong>[Patch 2020.06.19]</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/f1a0ca01f729f8ded49cd96f85c1b78a.avif?t=1593577428\" width=494 height=244 /></span><br><br><strong>Add New Game+</strong><br>-After clearing the game, Start the game again in New Game+ allows the selection of Hard Difficulty Mode and any equipments and upgrades made will remain.<br>(If you have cleared before this patch, load the existing save data and defeat the last boss again to unlock the New Game+ mode.)<br><br><strong>Add Hard Difficulty Mode</strong><br>-The enemies will be stronger/faster/more aggressive and the traps damage will increase in Hard Difficulty Mode.<br>-An additional Achievement has been added.<br><br><strong>Improve Air Mark Attack and Spell controll</strong><br>-Improved Mark Attack controll to make it easier to use in the air.<br>-Improved controll to use Spell during an attack or in the air.<br><br><strong>[Patch 2020.06.08]</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/e12c8ce14f3fc7835382de629d678501.avif?t=1593577428\" width=550 height=312 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/7f6e8fa485f3ac1f5854380f97b33cbd.avif?t=1593577428\" width=550 height=312 /></span><br><br>-When entering the stage, hidden items in the stage will be displayed.<br>-When exiting from the stage, items obtained from the stage and missed items are displayed.<br><br>-Bosses event cut scenes added.<br>-The <strong>Counter Attack Passive Rune</strong> added.<br>-An <strong>Achievement</strong> related to the Passive Rune added.<br><br><strong>[Patch 2020.06.02]</strong><br>- Fixed bugs that do not complete the achievement.<br>   --> If you have saved data, the achievement is completed automatically when you load that data.<br>- Some achievements Added.<br><br><strong>-Wider Field of View</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/2a5b86327a56b8ddbddb3542a2f3a7cd.avif?t=1593577428\" width=600 height=330 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/481d7805f3e049bcd140983c2234f692.avif?t=1593577428\" width=600 height=330 /></span><br><br><strong>[Patch 2020.05.28]</strong><br><strong>- Reduce niddles damage hit box</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/b152d7e8730150898c61ba39c3002983.avif?t=1593577428\" width=600 height=326 /></span><br><br><strong>- Simplify control of Wall-climbing</strong><br>-The player can immediately attach to the wall.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/730842baafce0849c37404d2e35dd16b.poster.avif?t=1593577428\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/730842baafce0849c37404d2e35dd16b.webm?t=1593577428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/730842baafce0849c37404d2e35dd16b.mp4?t=1593577428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>\"Karma knight\" is <strong> Not a Rogue-like game</strong>, is a <strong>oldschool vibe's 2d platform action game</strong>!<br><br>If you are interested in 2d platform action game, this is for you.<br>If you like to challenge, and stylish action, then this game is perfect for you!<br>“Karma Knight” is a 2D platform action game based on the concept of speed and stylish action. <br><br>Find hidden items in the stages, collect different spells, defeat the enemies <br>as you gain more experience and enjoy the overall platform action game style.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/cc397e54b43d48b25d3aa3e8c1bc7525.poster.avif?t=1593577428\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/cc397e54b43d48b25d3aa3e8c1bc7525.webm?t=1593577428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/cc397e54b43d48b25d3aa3e8c1bc7525.mp4?t=1593577428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Enjoy various platform actions.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/1c5ada2da01a76824541ee80d18df20f.poster.avif?t=1593577428\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/1c5ada2da01a76824541ee80d18df20f.webm?t=1593577428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/1c5ada2da01a76824541ee80d18df20f.mp4?t=1593577428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can attack enemies  in the air with MarkAttack.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/76167f4d156e7789417ac4baacfc9b11.poster.avif?t=1593577428\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/76167f4d156e7789417ac4baacfc9b11.webm?t=1593577428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/76167f4d156e7789417ac4baacfc9b11.mp4?t=1593577428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Various magic spells and attribute/passive rune system.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/e0a873f49d41068f2fa2e4095e3bafcc.poster.avif?t=1593577428\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/e0a873f49d41068f2fa2e4095e3bafcc.webm?t=1593577428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/e0a873f49d41068f2fa2e4095e3bafcc.mp4?t=1593577428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Enjoy various events and stories.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/82f197d2edac83b83b9a957e2c35fed8.poster.avif?t=1593577428\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/82f197d2edac83b83b9a957e2c35fed8.webm?t=1593577428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/82f197d2edac83b83b9a957e2c35fed8.mp4?t=1593577428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "\"Karma knight\" is <strong> Not a Rogue-like game</strong>, is a <strong>oldschool vibe's 2d platform action game</strong>!<br><br>If you are interested in 2d platform action game, this is for you.<br>If you like to challenge, and stylish action, then this game is perfect for you!<br>“Karma Knight” is a 2D platform action game based on the concept of speed and stylish action. <br><br>Find hidden items in the stages, collect different spells, defeat the enemies <br>as you gain more experience and enjoy the overall platform action game style.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/cc397e54b43d48b25d3aa3e8c1bc7525.poster.avif?t=1593577428\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/cc397e54b43d48b25d3aa3e8c1bc7525.webm?t=1593577428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/cc397e54b43d48b25d3aa3e8c1bc7525.mp4?t=1593577428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Enjoy various platform actions.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/1c5ada2da01a76824541ee80d18df20f.poster.avif?t=1593577428\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/1c5ada2da01a76824541ee80d18df20f.webm?t=1593577428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/1c5ada2da01a76824541ee80d18df20f.mp4?t=1593577428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can attack enemies  in the air with MarkAttack.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/76167f4d156e7789417ac4baacfc9b11.poster.avif?t=1593577428\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/76167f4d156e7789417ac4baacfc9b11.webm?t=1593577428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/76167f4d156e7789417ac4baacfc9b11.mp4?t=1593577428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Various magic spells and attribute/passive rune system.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/e0a873f49d41068f2fa2e4095e3bafcc.poster.avif?t=1593577428\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/e0a873f49d41068f2fa2e4095e3bafcc.webm?t=1593577428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/e0a873f49d41068f2fa2e4095e3bafcc.mp4?t=1593577428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Enjoy various events and stories.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/82f197d2edac83b83b9a957e2c35fed8.poster.avif?t=1593577428\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/82f197d2edac83b83b9a957e2c35fed8.webm?t=1593577428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255740/extras/82f197d2edac83b83b9a957e2c35fed8.mp4?t=1593577428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
